                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-05-06</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Second editions are always great. However, I find that I dont like all of the API reference in the book. I would rather look at APIs electronically and talk concepts in the book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Like the title says Java & XML</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
